author: HBO Max
description:
In Episode 4 of Peacemaker: The Official Podcast, James Gunn, Jennifer Holland (Emilia Harcourt), and Steve Agee (John Economos), and Freddie Stroma (Adrian Chase / Vigilante) break down the major moments of Peacemaker Season 1, Episode 4, "The Choad Less Traveled.” They dive into Vigilante’s character, explosive fight scenes, and the evolving character dynamics within the team. The episode’s emotional heart — Peacemaker’s complex and painful relationship with his father — is explored in depth, shedding light on the inner conflict driving his actions. The crew also unpacks the moral dilemmas and darker themes that surface as the story progresses. From stunt choreography to character development, Season 1, Episode 4 of the Peacemaker Podcast offers fans insight on one of the most pivotal chapters in the series. New episodes drop Mondays and Thursdays. Stream Peacemaker on HBO Max.
